snippet.title: Natalie Portman and Amber Heard's Make Up Artist on the Best Ind ie Beauty Products
snippet.description:
Natalie Portman and Amber Heard's Make-Up Artist on the Best Ind.ie Beauty Products.
Melanie Inglessis works her make up magic on some of Hollywood's most recognizable faces and is known for creating the perfect glow -- think Natalie Portman's smoky eyes and rose-tinted lips at the Golden Globes, Amber Heard's ultra-sultry red carpet glam and Kate Hudson's radiant and relaxed Fabletics campaigns. So when the annual Indie Beauty Expo, a traveling platform that hosts panel discussions and shows more 150 independent beauty brands to consumers, press, influencers and professions, hit downtown Los Angeles this week, Pret-a-Reporter could think of no better person to tour it on our behalf and share her must-try products. 

Check out the Parisian beauty guru's photo diary from the event and the products she loved, below. 

A post shared by Mélanie Inglessis (@melaniemakeup) on Jan 25, 2018 at 10:55am PST

Aenon’s
